Last Updated: November 1, 2025

FairSplitly respects your privacy. This app is designed to help users manage and split expenses easily, without collecting, storing, or sharing any personal information.

1. Data Collection

FairSplitly does not collect, store, or transmit any user data to external servers.
All information you enter (such as names, expenses, and totals) is stored locally on your device only and is never shared with us or any third parties.

2. Third-Party Services

FairSplitly does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs.
There are no integrations with social media, cloud services, or web APIs.

3. Purchases

FairSplitly is a one-time paid app. There are no subscriptions, no in-app purchases, and no ads.

4. Data Control

You have full control over your data.
All information is stored locally and can be permanently deleted at any time by uninstalling the app.

5. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

FairSplitly does not target or collect any data from children under 13 years of age.
